{"id": 3202, "title": "Ticket #3202: Schedd should advertise the \"home collector\"", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn a setup where a schedd is flocking to many different pools, it is impossible to tell which pool is the \"main\" pool which it is directly submitting to, and which it is flocking to.  For monitoring reasons, it is sometimes useful to make this distinction.  So, the schedd should advertise the main pool it is submitting to.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Sep-20 09:52</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/7ac71c43574c8f13809e3ac4818077e056320b29\">[33452]</a></span>: improve documentation of new schedd attribute <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=CollectorHost\" title=\"Collector Host\">CollectorHost</a></span> and add ticket number to version history item ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3202\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3202'); return false;\" title='Schedd should advertise the \"home collector\"'>#3202</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Aug-20 13:42</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/80085d3a30afb43cd67a6326e674ebb12512b702\">[33120]</a></span>: Document <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3202\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('320